16:07.732 --> 16:09.694
Like you're giving a life extension.

16:09.994 --> 16:13.217
You are now living in the life that Jesus Christ has given you.

16:13.637 --> 16:15.019
Share your time.

16:15.119 --> 16:15.760
I love this.

16:16.480 --> 16:18.322
This Friday night I was at our

16:18.434 --> 16:24.562
with our bunch of people from our church at the street team with the inner city church, Minneapolis with the life center.

16:24.582 --> 16:46.130
