17:23.921 --> 17:29.369
You share your time, you can't stop talking about what God's done when you're living on Lazarus time.

17:30.891 --> 17:35.677
Another thing like, now let me just, you steward your resources for God differently.

17:35.998 --> 17:41.345
Like when you're living on Lazarus time, things don't mean the same as they did before you were living on Lazarus time.

17:41.706 --> 17:44.850
