18:13.730 --> 18:18.256
In 2 Kings, chapter 20, verse one, we hear about a man by the name of Hezekiah, the king.

18:18.916 --> 18:26.085
It says about that time, Hezekiah became deathly ill, and the prophet Isaiah, son of Amos, Amos went to visit him.

18:26.366 --> 18:32.874
