21:39.402 --> 21:40.904
After this, there's going to be imprisonment.

21:41.144 --> 21:43.608
Your descendants are going into slavery.

21:43.648 --> 21:47.653
And everything you have is going to be wiped out after your 15-year extension, OK?

21:47.973 --> 21:49.115
So he gets that message.

21:49.135 --> 21:49.976
And then this is what it says.

21:50.216 --> 21:53.820
Then Hezekiah said, Isaiah, this message you have given me from the Lord is good.

21:54.321 --> 21:58.226
For the king was thinking, at least there will be peace and security during my lifetime.

22:00.002 --> 22:01.945
