27:34.552 --> 27:36.314
Like, I was dead!

27:36.554 --> 27:38.116
Oh, here he goes again, here he goes again.

27:38.837 --> 27:40.900
Four days, I was stinky dead, okay?

27:41.721 --> 27:45.586
So I just want you to understand, you live in that tension of Lazarus time.

27:46.018 --> 27:49.041
I wanna make the most of this, but it's okay to have joy.

27:49.081 --> 27:50.742
It's okay to have life.

27:51.183 --> 27:52.124
