27:52.344 --> 27:58.169
It's okay to live and enjoy the blessings and live blessed to be a blessing.

27:58.450 --> 28:00.972
Don't let the things that are a blessing in your life, they'll own you.

28:01.292 --> 28:04.315
Own those things and if God says, give them up, give them up, and move them around.

28:04.335 --> 28:05.316
Like, Lord, it's yours.

28:05.376 --> 28:06.637
If you want it, you can have it.

28:07.078 --> 28:10.501
And I'm gonna use it for your glory and for your honor.

28:11.422 --> 28:12.142
We wanna smile.

28:12.162 --> 28:12.983
We wanna live for God.

28:13.003 --> 28:14.044
We wanna enjoy life.

28:14.425 --> 28:15.986
We wanna make the most.

28:16.162 --> 28:17.884
of giving this Lazarus time.

28:19.225 --> 28:21.408
I pray that we find that rhythm of grace.

28:21.528 --> 28:29.576
And I can say one more time to Leslie, thank you for just letting us see that you prayed for an extension for Scott's life.

28:29.616 --> 28:33.861
And he got some extension, but it was just like Lazarus.

28:34.642 --> 28:37.324
Ultimately, Scott's life ended and he heard as well done.

28:38.446 --> 28:42.610
Each of us, no matter what we're facing in this life, we will always pray for every miracle.

28:43.106 --> 28:45.209
We will pray for every miracle and every need.

28:45.249 --> 28:46.911
We will always do that.

28:46.931 --> 28:53.400
And sometimes we get those Lazarus time extensions and sometimes we get moved into eternity and we hear our well done.

28:54.201 --> 29:00.630
But in between that moment and now I pray that every one of us would live making the most of Lazarus time.

29:00.650 --> 29:02.252
Let's make the most of these days.

29:02.713 --> 29:04.876
Listen to what Ephesians says, I close with this verse.

29:05.597 --> 29:06.698
So be careful how you live.

29:08.481 --> 29:12.466
Don't live like fools and if you could let me interject this like Hezekiah.

29:15.170 --> 29:25.067
live like fools, like those who are wise and if you let me interject this like Lazarus, make the most of every opportunity in these evil days.

29:26.469 --> 29:29.554
God, I want to thank you for the extension you've given me for life.

29:29.795 --> 29:34.803
Seriously, I wake up and I think, I've got a medal in my chest and it keeps me alive.

29:34.863 --> 29:36.446
Thank God for that.

29:36.466 --> 29:38.770
I'm living on Lazarus time.

29:40.066 --> 29:41.508
And I pray that we'll make the most of it.

29:41.528 --> 29:42.790
I pray that we'll open our mouth.

29:42.870 --> 29:44.152
We'll go on the global teams.

29:44.172 --> 29:46.014
We'll have gigantic giving goals.

29:46.054 --> 29:47.015
We'll feed orphans.

29:47.055 --> 29:48.157
We'll start churches.

29:48.257 --> 29:50.500
We'll rejoice in opposition.

29:50.520 --> 29:57.149
We'll open up our mouth and thank God for the opportunity to live every day for His glory and for His honor.

29:58.511 --> 29:59.172
Don't waste your life.

30:00.333 --> 30:01.415
Don't waste Lazarus' time.

30:02.536 --> 30:03.097
Don't waste it.

30:03.177 --> 30:04.279
We're in between here and there.

30:04.659 --> 30:05.721
And someday we're gonna die.

30:06.181 --> 30:07.663
And I pray between here and there.

30:08.104 --> 30:09.586
We live for the glory of God.

30:10.306 --> 30:12.509
So Lord, I just pray right now that you'd help us to live there.

30:13.730 --> 30:16.034
What a beautiful thing that Leslie just reminded us of.

30:16.054 --> 30:20.379
You spoke at Holy Spirit to her and you said, Lazarus just got an extension.

30:21.661 --> 30:23.303
And this life is so brief as it is.

30:23.744 --> 30:29.011
But when we get those extensions through miracles or our medicine, God, I pray that we'd make the most of it.

30:29.872 --> 30:32.856
And we'd not go back to living old ways, but we'd live differently.

30:32.916 --> 30:34.738
God, when we get the extension,

30:34.882 --> 30:40.308
through resurrection life, that you become the way, the truth, and the life to us, that our life has changed, and we're living differently.

30:40.348 --> 30:45.614
God, I pray that we live in that new resurrection time, living differently.

30:46.715 --> 30:48.457
Let's live in a way that honors you.

30:48.637 --> 30:51.560
So God, I pray that this message would go deep into all of us.

30:51.641 --> 30:55.925
We live differently, and we make the most of every day that you give us.

30:56.846 --> 30:58.028
In Jesus' name, I pray.

30:59.089 --> 31:00.210
Amen, and amen.

